{"title":"Brighten \u0026 Increase Radiance","description":"\u003cul\u003e\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003eTaza products are made for all skin types. We do, however, recommend to customers the products listed below, which are very beneficial for these specific skin concerns: reducing uneven skin and dark spots; instantly brightening skin tone; reducing dullness; and slight plumping effect for wrinkles and fine lines.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/2277\/9041\/files\/shutterstock_1095304445_480x480.jpg?v=1561398868\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003e \u003cb\u003eTaza Seaplex Anti Wrinkle Cream\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003eTaza Seaplex Anti-Wrinkle Cream can dramatically reduce the appearance of wrinkles on your skin. This cream is full of many vitamins and minerals, as well as other formidable ingredients that are extremely effective for your skin. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eTaza Vitamin C Serum \u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003eTaza Vitamin C Serum is essential for producing collagen, which is the substance that binds cells together. Stable collagen production is key to healthy, radiant, younger looking skin — it fights wrinkles and promotes evenness in the skin's tone and texture. Vitamin C has antioxidant properties to protect the skin from damaging free radicals as well. It also strengthens the skin's barrier, thickens the dermis, speeds up wound healing, and reduces inflammation. In high concentrations, it can reduce the appearance of skin discoloration.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTaza Tri-Peptide Serum \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003eTaza Tri-Peptide Serum helps increase collagen production providing significant anti-aging benefits. Not only does it encourage collagen production for more youthful skin, but also helps to reduce existing fine lines and wrinkles.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eTaza Eye \u0026amp; Neck Cream \u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003eThe skin around your eyes and neck is about ten times thinner than the rest of your face. With lower levels of collagen and elastin fibers, the eyes and neck are the first areas to give away one's age. For the eyes, aging may appear in the form of crow’s feet and drooping upper eyelids - making your eyes appear smaller. Taza Eye \u0026amp; Neck Cream contains two important peptides to combat this: Hyloxyl and Matrixyl. Matrixyl is a well-known peptide that reduces the appearance of wrinkles. Hyloxyl is a top ingredient that reduces the appearance of dark circles.\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"taza-seaplex-anti-aging-facial-cream","title":"Taza Natural Seaplex Anti-Aging Facial Cream","description":"\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: small;\" size=\"6\"\u003e*Free Standard Shipping\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e; \u003cem\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: small;\" size=\"6\"\u003e*Orders from this site Fulfillment by Amazon.ca;\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e \u003cem\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: small;\" size=\"6\"\u003e*Secure \u0026amp; Protected Cardholder Data Processing with Shopify Payments\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTaza Natural Seaplex Anti-Aging Cream\u003c\/strong\u003e contains: Jojoba Oil, Avocado Oil, Grapeseed Oil, Shea Butter, Vitamin E, Grapeseed Extract, Wild Mushroom Extract, Japanese Green Tea Extract, and Cucumber Extract. The following are benefits of these ingredients:\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003